:21:"2017-09-20 1:10pm GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2015-02-06";s:8:"homepage";s:67:"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder";s:8:"sections";a:5:{s:11:"description";s:1525:"<p>YITH Woocommerce Review Reminder allows you to send, after 7 days the order status is set to &#171;Completed&#187;, a reminder to customers with an invitation to make a review of the items purchased.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Select mail type (HTML or plain text)</li>\n<li>Customize email subject</li>\n<li>Customize email content using a wide set of options</li>\n<li>Use blocklist to add and manage users who do not want to receive further requests.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href="http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Варианты</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder, you can <a href="mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder.</p>\n<h3>Переводчики</h3>\n<h4>Доступные языки</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n<li>Italian</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress" title="Translating WordPress" rel="nofollow">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href="http://yithemes.com/contact/" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder languages.</p>\n";s:12:"installation";s:736:"<h4>Установка</h4>\n<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode plugin.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Настройки</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder will add a new tab called &#171;Review Reminder&#187; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n";s:9:"changelog";s:3583:"<h4>Version 1.3.3 &#8212; Released: Sept 20, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: WPML support on unsubscribe link and page</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.1 &#8212; Released: May 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: review requested when comments are closed</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.0 &#8212; Released: Mar 16, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Support for WooCommerce 2.7.0-RC 1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8212; Released: Jun 01, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Support for WooCommerce 2.6.0 beta 3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 &#8212; Released: May 06, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: wc_get_template_html() for versions of WooCommerce before 2.5.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.9 &#8212; Released: Apr 18, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: custom email template not rendering</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.8 &#8212; Released: Apr 15, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: unsubscribe link placeholder</li>\n<li>New: minified version of CSS files</li>\n<li>Fix: table creation for multisite installation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.7 &#8212; Released: Feb 12, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: email not scheduling</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.6 &#8212; Released: Feb 3, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: get email status on sending</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.5 &#8212; Released: Feb 1, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: test email sending</li>\n<li>New: search field on &#171;Blocklist&#187; tab</li>\n<li>Update: language files</li>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n<li>Fix: JS code improvements</li>\n<li>Fix: minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.4 &#8212; Released: Jan 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.3 &#8212; Released: Dec 28, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: italian translation file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8212; Released: Dec 11, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: unsubscribe page initialization makes conflict with some plugin</li>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8212; Released: Nov 02, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed text domain from ywrr to yith-woocommerce-review-reminder</li>\n<li>Update: changed all language file for the new text domain</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8212; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.9 &#8212; Released: Oct 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: italian language file</li>\n<li>Update: core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.8 &#8212; Released: Sept 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: new file class-yith-custom-table.php</li>\n<li>Remove: old file class-yith-ywrr-custom-table.php</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.7 &#8212; Released: Sept 02, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: class-yith-ywrr-custom-table.php not found error</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.6 &#8212; Released: Sept 01, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 &#8212; Released: Aug 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce #1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8212; Released: Aug 13, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin core framework</li>\n<li>Fix: minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8212; Released: May 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Screen options for Blocklist table</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8212; Released: Apr 17, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Redirection bug in &#171;Blocklist&#187; tab bulk actions</li>\n<li>Fix: E-mail template management</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8212; Released: Feb 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Woocommerce 2.3 support</li>\n<li>Tweak: String translation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8212; Released: Feb 06, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Первый релиз</li>\n</ul>\n";s:3:"faq";s:782:"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<h4>Установка</h4>\n<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode plugin.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Настройки</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder will add a new tab called &#171;Review Reminder&#187; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n</p>\n\n";s:11:"screenshots";s:979:"<ol><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625678"><img src="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625678" alt="&lt;p&gt;This is the mail settings page for the plugin, you can find it inside the YIT Plugins menu item. You can configure the mail with the review reminder.&lt;/p&gt;"></a><p><p>This is the mail settings page for the plugin, you can find it inside the YIT Plugins menu item. You can configure the mail with the review reminder.</p></p></li><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625678"><img src="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625678" alt="&lt;p&gt;This is the blocklist page for the plugin. You can add or remove users from the blocklist.&lt;/p&gt;"></a><p><p>This is the blocklist page for the plugin. You can add or remove users from the blocklist.</p></p></li></ol>";}s:17:"short_desc