:7:"ratings";a:5:{i:5;i:7;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:8;}s:11:"num_ratings";i:16;s:15:"support_threads";i:0;s:24:"support_threads_resolved";i:0;s:15:"active_installs";i:1000;s:10:"downloaded";i:13458;s:12:"last_updated";s:22:"2017-10-12 12:40pm GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2015-04-07";s:8:"homepage";s:65:"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list";s:8:"sections";a:5:{s:11:"description";s:1943:"<p>What do you do when you have no more stock of one of your products and your customers want to buy it? You risk to lose them, unless you make a system available for them to be notified of the product coming back to stock. Then, why not using a plugin that allows them to be added to a waiting list and being informed in an automatic and efficient way? This is what YITH WooCommerce Waiting List does, allowing you to loyalise them in a simple way and at the same time not lose them.</p>\n<p><strong>Main features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A form to receive a reminding email when the item is back in stock</li>\n<li>&#171;Add me to the waiting list&#187; button for logged users</li>\n<li>Summary metabox with the number of waiting user and a rapid way to contact them</li>\n<li>Customization of the &#171;Notify me&#187; button</li>\n<li>Email basic template to notify users for an item back in stock</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Варианты</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Waiting List, you can <a href="mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List.</p>\n<h3>Переводчики</h3>\n<h4>Доступные языки</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you can&#8217;t find this plugin in your language and want to translate it, use the dedicated tool at <a href="https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/it/default/wp-plugins/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list" title="Translating WordPress" rel="nofollow">Translating WordPress</a>.<br />\nOr, if you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send it as an email attachment from our [Contacts page] (http://yithemes.com/contact/ &#171;Your Inspiration Themes&#187;) and we will bundle into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List.</p>\n";s:12:"installation";s:241:"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n";s:3:"faq";s:448:"<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;s compatible with WooCommerce?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Yes, of course. This plugin is full compatible with WooCommerce 2.3 and previous version 2.2.</p>\n\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n";s:9:"changelog";s:2553:"<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<p>Released Oct 12 &#8212; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.2.0.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.8.2</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<p>Released Apr 21 &#8212; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.4.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Prevent duplicated post meta for product.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<p>Released Mar 29 &#8212; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0 RC2.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.3.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<p>Released Jan 13 &#8212; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Shortcode for print waiting list form [yith_wcwtl_form].</li>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6.7.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.1.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Dev: Add filter for form html &#8216;yith_wcwtl