ct-vendors/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1460902";}s:12:"contributors";a:0:{}}}s:41:"yith-woocommerce-colors-labels-variations";a:10:{s:4:"name";s:43:"YITH WooCommerce Color and Label Variations";s:4:"slug";s:41:"yith-woocommerce-colors-labels-variations";s:15:"premium_constat";a:2:{i:0;s:17:"YITH_WCCL_PREMIUM";i:1;s:17:"YITH_WAPO_PREMIUM";}s:11:"premium-url";s:43:"yith-woocommerce-color-and-label-variations";s:11:"premium-dir";s:39:"yith-woocommerce-color-label-variations";s:17:"short_description";s:140:"The best way to offer a complete overview on all options available for your products: with one plugin only you can add unlimited variations.";s:7:"version";s:5:"1.2.6";s:12:"last_updated";s:10:"2017-04-01";s:10:"repository";s:4:"yith";s:4:"file";s:8:"init.php";}s:32:"yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons";a:5:{s:4:"name";s:32:"YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons";s:4:"slug";s:32:"yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons";s:15:"premium_constat";s:17:"YITH_WAPO_PREMIUM";s:4:"file";s:8:"init.php";s:7:"wp_info";a:27:{s:4:"name";s:32:"YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons";s:4:"slug";s:32:"yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons";s:7:"version";s:5:"1.0.6";s:6:"author";s:43:"<a href="http://yithemes.com/">YITHEMES</a>";s:14:"author_profile";s:39:"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes";s:8:"requires";s:3:"4.4";s:6:"tested";s:5:"4.7.7";s:12:"requires_php";b:0;s:6:"rating";d:70;s:7:"ratings";a:5:{i:5;i:4;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:2;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:2;}s:11:"num_ratings";i:8;s:15:"support_threads";i:9;s:24:"support_threads_resolved";i:0;s:15:"active_installs";i:3000;s:10:"downloaded";i:23239;s:12:"last_updated";s:21:"2017-04-06 3:18pm GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2016-05-20";s:8:"homepage";s:0:"";s:8:"sections";a:5:{s:11:"description";s:2503:"<p>With YITH WooCommerce Product Add-ons you&#8217;ll be able to increase your customers&#8217; propensity to spend more and you&#8217;ll be able to cut off time dedicated to managing additional options for each product separately. How? Let&#8217;s imagine you have a jewellery store and one of your customers is going to purchase a ring: if variations can let them decide whether they prefer it in gold, silver or copper, how can you let them have a brief sentence carved on it and associate an extra cost to this in product page? YITH Product Add-ons allows you either to add a text field where your users can enter their sentence or select the one you have already configured for them through checkboxes or radio buttons in product page. And you&#8217;ll forget about long and messy email correspondences where the risk to mix up orders from different customers is just around the corner.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create groups of options And choose to use them for all products of the shop, only for specific categories or limited on a single product</li>\n<li>Choose from different options Checkbox and Radio button</li>\n<li>Set dependency between the options To show a dropdown option only to users who selected the one that depends on it</li>\n<li>Increase the cost of product by assigning a fixed price to any of the options selected by user</li>\n<li>Specify single options By setting label and description</li>\n<li>Show a tooltip for the product add-ons</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have any suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons, you can <a href="mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;" title="Your Inspiration\nThemes">write us</a><br />\nso we can bundle them into the next plugin release.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<p>If you can&#8217;t find this plugin in your language and want to translate it, use the dedicated tool at [Translating WordPress] (https://translate<br />\n.wordpress.org/locale/it/default/wp-plugins/yith-pre-order-for-woocommerce &#171;Translating WordPress&#187;).<br />\nOr, if you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send it as an email attachment from our [Contacts page] (http://yithemes.com/contact/ &#171;Your Inspiration Themes&#187;) and we will bundle into YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons.</p>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n<li>Italian</li>\n</ul>\n";s:12:"installation";s:641:"<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons to be working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons will add a new tab called &#171;Products Add-Ons&#187; in &#171;YIT Plugins&#187; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n";s:3:"faq";s:1352:"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons to be working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons will add a new tab called &#171;Products Add-Ons&#187; in &#171;YIT Plugins&#187; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I add options groups on variable products?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, the plugin allows to do it. Options can be configured globally on product, but not on single variation.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I disable global options on single product?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can do it, but not singularly. From the product editing page, you can disable the use of &#171;all&#187; global options groups.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>I would like to show an option only when a specific combination of options chosen from users occurs. How can I do it?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You must enable the dependency on the option you are interested in by inserting the name of options you want your users to select.</p>\n</p>\n\n";s:9:"changelog";s:672:"<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Plugin framework</li>\n<li>Fix: Failed opening &#8216;yit-woocommerce-compatibility.php&#8217; error</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: WooCommerce 3.0 support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: WordPress 4.7 support</li>\n<li>Fixed: clicking label radio and checkbox buttons doesn&#8217; t selected</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: checkbox issue with &#171;the edge/internet explorer&#187;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Conflict with &#171;Advanced Recent Posts&#187; plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Notice when WooCommerce is not activated</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<p>Initial Release</p>\n";s:11:"screenshots";s:943:"<ol><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1629221"><img src="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1629221" alt="Setting Options"></a><p>Setting Options</p></li><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1629221"><img src="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1629221" alt="YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in &quot;Add-Ons&quot; edit page"></a><p>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in "Add-Ons" edit page</p></li><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1629221"><img src="https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1629221" alt="YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in &quot;Single Prodcut&quot; page"></a><p>YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in "Single Prodcut" page</p></li></ol>";}s:17:"short_description";s:99:"Increase average order value by letting your customers purchase additional options on your products";s:13:"download_link";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.6.zip";s:11:"screenshots";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:85:"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1629221";s:7:"caption";s:15:"Setting Options";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:85:"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1629221";s:7:"caption";s:55:"YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in "Add-Ons" edit page";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:85:"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1629221";s:7:"caption";s:57:"YITH WooCommerce Product Add-Ons in "Single Prodcut" page";}}s:4:"tags";a:4:{s:15:"product-add-ons";s:15:"product add-ons";s:11:"woocommerce";s:11:"woocommerce";s:35:"woocommerce-advanced-product-option";s:35:"woocommerce advanced product option";s:27:"woocommerce-product-add-ons";s:27:"woocommerce product add-ons";}s:8:"versions";a:8:{s:5:"1.0.0";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.0.zip";s:5:"1.0.1";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.1.zip";s:5:"1.0.2";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.2.zip";s:5:"1.0.3";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.3.zip";s:5:"1.0.4";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.4.zip";s:5:"1.0.5";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.5.zip";s:5:"1.0.6";s:81:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.1.0.6.zip";s:5:"trunk";s:75:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-product-add-ons.zip";}s:11:"donate_link";s:0:"";s:5:"icons";a:1:{s:2:"1x";s:85:"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-product-add-on